text: George Wheeler (December 14, 1914 - July 8, 1990) was an American gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:1990 deaths Category:American male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of the United States Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Pittsburgh
